body:
Do you have an example net which is failing to checkpoint because of this? My guess is that it's because Sequential only supports single argument forwards. But maybe even better implementation is:

```
def run_function(start, end, functions):
        def forward(input):
            for j in range(start, end + 1):
                input = functions[j](input)
            return input
        return forward
```
